  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Book and Unlock Exclusive Savings</h2>
<p>Book a walking holiday with us, and unlock exclusive savings from some of our favourite brands.</p>
<p><img src="/media/13086359/summer-2021-benefits.jpeg" alt="Summer Exclusive Benefits" data-udi="umb://media/2b38b86706014abca2c651c371fa2217" /></p>
<h3>Step Into These Savings</h3>
<p>When you book a walking holiday with us, you’re not just setting your sights on a fantastic getaway, you’re also walking right into exclusive discounts from some of our favourite brands.</p>
<p>Trek smart and dress sharper with discounts on outdoor clothing and equipment from Cotswold Outdoor.</p>
<p>Want to know which way is north (or where the nearest coffee spot is)? We also offer special rates on Cicerone walking maps and guides, as well as discounted courier services.</p>
<p><strong>Take advantage of these fantastic offers:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Save 20% with Cicerone</strong></li>
<li><strong>15% Discount with Pecksniff's</strong></li>
<li><strong>Up to 35% Discount with APH<br /></strong></li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__header">Save 20% on Cicerone Walking Guides</div>
<div class="c-card__header"></div>
<div class="c-card__header"><span><strong><img src="/media/13067778/cicerone-discount-with-inghams-lakes-and-mountains.jpg?width=487&amp;height=233&amp;mode=max" alt="Inghams Discount with Cicerone" width="487" height="233" data-udi="umb://media/cabd60afa8d24220ad72ed4aefadd4c1" /></strong></span></div>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p>We're big fans of Cicerone’s extensive range of walking guides, which have been helping us explore Europe for nearly 50 years.</p>
<p>They have over 350 different walking guidebooks, many providing detailed information on some of our favourite walking destinations.</p>
<p>Book with us, and we’ll send you a voucher code to use.</p>
<p><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.cicerone.co.uk/" target="_blank" title="Cicerone walking guides" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">View Website </a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__header">
<p>15% Discount with Pecksniff's</p>
</div>
<div class="c-card__img"><img style="width: 451px; height: 243px;" src="/media/13100850/pecksniffs.png?width=451&amp;height=243" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/ff59c0bb37644e18ac49bbdcc9b055e9" /></div>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p>Pecksniff’s have been creating inspiring products from their Brighton boutique for over 30 years. Their inspiring fragrances are created through a mixture of master perfumery skills and innovative cosmetic science.</p>
<p>Book with us, and we’ll send you a voucher code to use.</p>
<p><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.pecksniffsshop.com/" target="_blank" title="Pecksniff shop" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">View Website </a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__content">
<div class="c-card__header">Up to 35% Discount with APH</div>
<p>We've teamed up with APH to provide our guests with excellent rates on airport services including airport car parking, hotels and lounges.</p>
<p>Pre-book with APH and save up to 35% on the cost of your airport parking.</p>
<a rel="noopener" href="https://www.aph.com/?campaign_code=GAPH101&amp;gclid=EAIaIQobChMIw-yQsu_L3QIVyed3Ch2V-QpIEAAYASAAEgKtxfD_BwE" target="_blank" title="APH" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="?campaign_code=GAPH101&amp;gclid=EAIaIQobChMIw-yQsu_L3QIVyed3Ch2V-QpIEAAYASAAEgKtxfD_BwE">View Website</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-image">
<div class="c-card__img"><span><strong><a href="https://www.aph.com/?campaign_code=GAPH101&amp;gclid=EAIaIQobChMIw-yQsu_L3QIVyed3Ch2V-QpIEAAYASAAEgKtxfD_BwE" title="aph.com" data-anchor="?campaign_code=GAPH101&amp;gclid=EAIaIQobChMIw-yQsu_L3QIVyed3Ch2V-QpIEAAYASAAEgKtxfD_BwE"><img src="/media/13070433/inghams-special-offers-with-aph.jpg?width=517&amp;height=247&amp;mode=max" alt="35% with Inghams on APH airport car parking" width="517" height="247" data-udi="umb://media/f5cca846ec4d4ded8f30883721974b41" /></a></strong></span></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
